A large workshop in back that appeals to the person that likes to work on things. Put your personal touch on this home to make it yours. Located in picturesque Marshallville. Near I-75 and just minutes away from shopping, medical facilities and RAFB. This one will not last long. Call me today for your personal showing appointment.
